      "source": [
        "### 12. 1列目をcol1.txtに，2列目をcol2.txtに保存\n",
        "各行の1列目だけを抜き出したものをcol1.txtに，2列目だけを抜き出したものをcol2.txtとしてファイルに保存せよ．確認にはcutコマンドを用いよ．"
      ]
    },
    {
      "metadata": {
        "id": "-rYDTN7PnLZ2",
        "colab_type": "code",
        "colab": {}
      },
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "column1, column2 = [], []\n",
        "\n",
        "with open('/content/hightemp.txt', 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n",
        "  for line in f:\n",
        "    columns = line.rstrip().split('\\t')\n",
        "    column1.append(columns[0])\n",
        "    column2.append(columns[1])\n",
        "    \n",
        "with open('/content/col1.txt', 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n",
        "  f.write('\\n'.join(column1))\n",
        "  \n",
        "with open('/content/col2.txt', 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n",
        "  f.write('\\n'.join(column2))\n",
        "  "
      ],
      "execution_count": 0,
      "outputs": []
    },
