        "### 13. col1.txtとcol2.txtをマージ\n",
        "12で作ったcol1.txtとcol2.txtを結合し，元のファイルの1列目と2列目をタブ区切りで並べたテキストファイルを作成せよ．確認にはpasteコマンドを用いよ．"
      ]
    },
    {
      "metadata": {
        "id": "yQI_Pumr5K0f",
        "colab_type": "code",
        "colab": {}
      },
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "with open('col1.txt', 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f, open('col2.txt', 'r', encoding='utf-8') as g, open('merge_file.txt', 'w', encoding='utf-8') as mf:\n",
        "  for c1, c2 in zip(f, g):\n",
        "    mf.write(f'{c1.rstrip()}\\t{c2.rstrip()}\\n')\n"
      ],
      "execution_count": 0,
      "outputs": []
    },
