      "source": [
        "### 14. 先頭からN行を出力\n",
        "自然数Nをコマンドライン引数などの手段で受け取り，入力のうち先頭のN行だけを表示せよ．確認にはheadコマンドを用いよ．"
      ]
    },
    {
      "metadata": {
        "id": "qqBavoBIi5wC",
        "colab_type": "code",
        "colab": {}
      },
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "def disp_head(filename, lines):\n",
        "  with open(filename, 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n",
        "    for _, c in zip(range(lines), f):\n",
        "      print(c, end='')\n",
        "  return"
      ],
      "execution_count": 0,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "metadata": {
        "id": "-7x67dYomFv6",
        "colab_type": "code",
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/",
          "height": 187
        },
        "cellView": "both",
        "outputId": "f5bc8d57-a214-43d6-fbf7-11418e575035"
      },
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "filename = 'hightemp.txt' #@param {type:\"string\"}\n",
        "lines = 10 #@param {type:\"integer\"}\n",
        "\n",
        "disp_head(filename, lines)"
      ],
      "execution_count": 26,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
